Generalizations and aggregations are two specific structural relationships,

2
00:00:04,780 --> 00:00:09,230
between classes. More general, is the idea of association. For

3
00:00:09,230 --> 00:00:14,490
example, went to school at, is an association between the university class and

4
00:00:14,490 --> 00:00:19,760
the student class. Stative verbs, denote a state of being. For example,

5
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:25,290
the house sits on top of a hill. Stative verbs, often indicate associations.

6
00:00:25,290 --> 00:00:28,530
In class models, associations are indicated by lines connecting

7
00:00:28,530 --> 00:00:32,540
the associated classes. There are no special adornments on the ends, but

8
00:00:32,540 --> 00:00:35,840
the line is usually labeled with the name, of the association.
